sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as Member
  participant W as Web App
  participant A as API
  participant E as EventDB
  participant P as Projector
  participant R as Read Model

  U->>W: Submit signup form
  W->>A: POST /v1/auth/signup
  A->>E: append member.auth.created
  A->>P: run projection
  P->>R: upsert rm_member_auth

  U->>W: Buy membership package
  W->>A: POST subscription command
  A->>E: append subscription.activated
  A->>P: run projection
  P->>R: upsert rm_subscription_active

  U->>W: Confirm payment
  W->>A: POST payment confirm
  A->>E: append payment.confirmed
  A->>P: run projection
  P->>R: update rm_payment_queue + rm_dashboard

  U->>W: Check-in request
  W->>A: POST checkin
  A->>R: verify active subscription
  A-->>W: Eligible / rejected
